# Per-user custom integrations — each system keeps its own custom integration code
# here (GoHighLevel, email, CRM, etc.). The umbrella auto-discovers apps/*, so this
# compiles and runs locally but stays out of the shared repo. Custom integrations
# should depend on Arbor's public facades, not internals.
apps/arbor_integrations/